beer.beer_name: GB x Beddy Rays Beddy Hayze
beer.beer_description: We love playing music and drinking beer - the two go together like jam and pikelets. You wouldn't trust us to brew the stuff though, that's why we've teamed up with our mates at Green Beacon to bring you something special to wrap your laughing gear around. Rip the lid off a tin and join us in celebrating "Beddy Hayze" Hazy Pale.
